snippet.title: Survival Run for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
...and I ran.
I ran so far away.
I just ran.
I ran all night and day.
I couldn't get away.

Sorry, I just couldn't resist. :P

Anyways, Survival Run is an okay game, but the doors are confusing. If you want to go the left, you have to choose the right door and vice-versa. That goes a rating down.
